usage: verify_stage6_bundle.py [-h] [--stage6-md STAGE6_MD]
                               [--h1-run-dir H1_RUN_DIR]
                               [--h2-run-dir FINAL_PACK_RUN_DIR]
                               [--h4-run-dir H4_RUN_DIR] [--only-h1]
                               [--only-h2] [--only-h3] [--only-h4] [--skip-md]
                               [--skip-h1] [--skip-h2] [--skip-h3] [--skip-h4]

Verify the compact Stage-6 theorem bundle.

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --stage6-md STAGE6_MD
                        Bundle theorem markdown
  --h1-run-dir H1_RUN_DIR
                        H1 raw artifact directory
  --h2-run-dir, --final-pack-run-dir FINAL_PACK_RUN_DIR
                        H2 raw artifact directory
  --h4-run-dir H4_RUN_DIR
                        H4 raw artifact directory
  --only-h1             Run only the H1 artifact audit
  --only-h2, --only-certpack-final
                        Run only the H2 pure-frontier artifact audit
  --only-h3             Run only the PAB/row-complement witness sanity check
  --only-h4             Run only the H4 signed-cancellation artifact audit
  --skip-md             Skip stage6.md theorem-text sanity check
  --skip-h1             Skip H1 artifact audit
  --skip-h2             Skip H2 pure-frontier artifact audit
  --skip-h3             Skip PAB/row-complement witness sanity check
  --skip-h4             Skip H4 signed-cancellation artifact audit
